&lt;p&gt;Dental Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for x 2 fulltime GDC registered dental nurses to work as part of the Community &amp; Specialist Dental Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to recruit an enthusiastic and motivated dental nurse to work alongside our team of consultant, specialists and community dental officers, dental therapists and experienced dental nurses. You will deliver high quality dental nursing care for all types of dental patients and as well as carrying out administrative duties.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need a flexible approach to working across our sites in Hammersmith &amp; Fulham, Kensington &amp; Chelsea and Westminster.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We encourage our staff to develop, be innovative and utilise their skills and knowledge to support and improve services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are hardworking, empathic and compassionate then this is the role for you.&lt;/p&gt;
